OL,3,CSyrian shopkeeper's second chance at
OL,4,Cgrocery store dreams after racist
OL,5,Cattack
OL,7,FSyrian shopkeeper Ahmad Alkhamran has
OL,8,Ffinally welcomed customers into his
OL,9,FFalls Road grocery store after being
OL,10,Fintimidated out of south Belfast.
OL,12,FMr Alkhamran had fitted out a grocery
OL,13,Fstore on Donegall Road last September
OL,14,Fbut before it opened, the shop was the
OL,15,Ftarget of four racist attacks in two
OL,16,Fweeks.
OL,18,FSix months later, the shop owner has
OL,19,Fopened a new store on the Falls Road.
