OL,7,FWhile initially feeling nervous about
OL,8,Fstarting over after his first shop was
OL,9,Fdestroyed, Ahmad was given a boost by
OL,10,Fthe Falls Road community who gave him
OL,11,Fa warm welcome.
OL,13,F"The community here, they helped me. A
OL,14,Flot of different people call me, some
OL,15,Fpeople they come to my house and show
OL,16,Ftheir solidarity. It gives me
OL,17,Fsomething very very positive to leave
OL,18,Fthe past... to look for the future.
OL,19,FWhen I see that, the support around
OL,20,Fme, I keep going and I find my place
OL,21,Fhere."
