OL,7,FLocal SDLP councillor Paul Doherty
OL,8,Fhelped Ahmad set up on the Falls Road.
OL,10,F"One of the first things we did when
OL,11,Fwe got the keys to the premises was
OL,12,Fwalk around the community and knock
OL,13,Fdoors and the welcome he got from
OL,14,Fpeople in this community was
OL,15,Fabsolutely heartwarming.
