OL,7,F"It gave him a real lift, his head was
OL,8,Fdown, he went through a traumatic
OL,9,Fexperience on Donegall Road, Ahmad has
OL,10,Fgone through a traumatic experience
OL,11,Fthroughout his life in terms of
OL,12,Ffleeing Syria as well, so he didn't
OL,13,Fdeserve what he went through in south
OL,14,FBelfast but for him to go through this
OL,15,Fhere and this real positivity and a
OL,16,Fcommunity really coming together and
OL,17,Frallying round him, it's just such a
OL,18,Fbeautiful thing to see."
